{"tid":1816981,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［不捉鬼＝不分化？］鬼，或成瓦解運動的關鍵。","createTime":"2020-01-08T16:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T03:14:24.000Z","uid":112589,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"67e5b3f929527daf3b921d203859c7941ba8b3f6","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:35:09.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇完將軍澳full gear手足比幾個喬裝狗捉，冇一個人願意去救佢，全部跑到保特咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家捉鬼最大嘅問題！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過往d on9仔亂捉鬼辣㷫過手足好多次，一嚟係亂鳩咁話人係鬼，大隻係鬼、戴耳機係鬼、多gear係鬼等等，二嚟你地d態度差撚到直當咗佢係鬼，完全冇根據咁篤人出嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最新個單我信佢係真手足，裝修緊係絕對唔應該捉，就算佢係狗都係幫緊手搞d中資，你唔認同嘅無視就算，唔好間接曝露手足嘅身份。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n鬼呢個問題，係近呢幾個星期嘅活動越趨嚴峻。一直咁樣落去就算我地心裡默念「不捉鬼」，對彼此嘅信住都會慢慢消失。<br />\n<br />\n我地一直都堅持「不捉鬼」呢個理念，亦有人引述曹操嘅故事嚟講，認為對家放鬼入嚟主要嘅目的係分化，我地要唔好中佢嘅陷阱就係「不捉鬼」嚟達至我地「不分化」，但咁諗又係咪適用於我地嘅情況呢？。曹操之所以可以咁做，最大嘅原因係佢地嘅陣營係有一定程定嘅武力，咁做亦係一個心理戰。大家諗諗我地呢邊，我地面對面同班狗打會有贏嘅機會咩？大家心裡有數。基於武力嘅不對等，我地唔可以用傳統嘅方式同佢地鬥。<br />\n<br />\n其實我地一直叫大家唔好捉鬼唔好捉鬼唔好捉鬼，但係偏偏d鬼搞到我地拉咗好多手足。<br />\n大家可以再睇番近日嘅直播片，佢地基本上係大規模放鬼，已經唔同之前一兩隻可以由得佢，因為咁少做唔到d咩。<br />\n<br />\n咁我地再諗下，點解佢地會越放越多鬼。<br />\n原因只有一個，因為冇後果。<br />\n每次放鬼行動都成功拉到人，次次都全身而退，一d損失都冇，又可以搞到班黑衣暴徒自己打自己。<br />\n<br />\n不捉鬼，唔代表我地就能夠團結一致，唔代表鬼係唔存在，反而鬼仲可以好安心咁執行佢嘅任務。<br />\n佢諗住我地以後唔會捉鬼，我地就倒行逆施，捉比佢睇，仲表明一定會捉到。<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地只要成功一次，比佢地知道做鬼嘅下場。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔需要打死佢，但係要有阻嚇性，一定要直搗佢地嘅尊嚴，除撚佢地d衫，用索帶綁佢係條電燈柱到。<br />\n你估咁樣玩法人民日報、文匯報可以點樣寫？香港警察被黑衣暴徒剝光豬遊街示眾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知呢個係咪最好嘅方法，但係至少我覺得比佢地用鬼拉得越嚟越多人我真係睇唔過眼，我地一定要正面去解決呢個困局。<br />\n<br />\n我地必須約法三章。<br />\n如何有效捉鬼，點樣唔會引起太多人注目。<br />\n<br />\n少少愚見<br />\n1. 儘量唔好搞全黑full gear嘅手足<br />\n2. 有懷疑嘅時候，觀察觀察觀察，跟住佢行去邊做緊咩。睇定d先，唔好一嚟就「阿sir, 委任證呢？」<br />\n3. 態度好少少，有禮貌d。（你一日確認唔到佢係狗，佢都係手足。）<br />\n4. 手足如果察覺到好多人𥄫住自己懷疑你係鬼，不妨上前主動同其他手足溝通下，相信如果真係鬼嘅話絕對唔會主動解釋自己身份。<br />\n5. 確認前唔好要求佢除罩。<br />\n<br />\n利申：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我預咗會比人屌架啦，但係起碼都係一個方法。期望大家集思廣益。<br />\n<br />\n附上曹操故事link<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1723153/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1723153/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c48d050e551b36d42b5df3a36d75998f2b590233","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:36:07.000Z","msg":"樓主就係鬼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc988d604e6618f9114a853305d2c8265e9925d8","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:37:01.000Z","msg":"捉鬼撚死全家"},{"pid":"668fd0025931608344b45855e5b057efc7fa511b","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:37:32.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"b28247508d9da49b6c30987cf0b94062ff2a7bcf","tid":1816981,"uid":84176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:38:32.000Z","msg":"一係唔捉，一捉就要捉真鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f262d2e5a55e6dcefd9445813151214d307a23","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:38:55.000Z","msg":"好想見到剝光豬嘅阿sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3fc33410da285486e850ea7a2b11879a7d07fe4","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b28247508d9da49b6c30987cf0b94062ff2a7bcf","tid":1816981,"uid":84176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:38:32.000Z","msg":"一係唔捉，一捉就要捉真鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:40:49.000Z","msg":"所以要諗多方法嚟去搵d冚家剷出嚟，而又唔好搞到手足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729b844ec1cf64c7a28c89cbcd00fee14c925a12","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:41:57.000Z","msg":"好少出po，一嚟打咁多字。唔同意都入嚟比粒膠我，或者鬧下我都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a144f49d4b21e0bb62a0c50de2045f6277e6aee7","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:44:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef478d1f572d8f48bfa122373aedd30ee2ca3d2d","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:45:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8b1b186f19302d2bcc1f1519d4cd1bff4dddc9b9","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:45:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d4f5c8745b78dbabe9f6843280a5669a4eeaef24","tid":1816981,"uid":278180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:46:20.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"afc48a6331e33ca318a60e645a7c42dd4ce70ba6","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:48:03.000Z","msg":"大大力推"},{"pid":"edf5d134384842ef0489ff58cd4bd6b43b7918f5","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"除衫！除衫！除衫！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c992163c574ecafe933fa5e63babff7e3a8ecc72","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:54:44.000Z","msg":"認真post冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf14f6e92c610a84c64558a196992503b0daa0f","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:59:13.000Z","msg":"唔好鳩捉ok?"},{"pid":"07f15ae37180666bb226f650bc18d32bba411324","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:01:55.000Z","msg":"push push push"},{"pid":"bbbf33a5ea94623b6d56466efab5d532ff9e0204","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"屌，單機推咗成頁"},{"pid":"8890ce73748446ee9e4c5801ecf5d781818e15e7","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:05:41.000Z","msg":"人嚟啊"},{"pid":"6b85d59fe65127175b6abef75bce1f385918346f","tid":1816981,"uid":308771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:10:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4981e7eaeb16e987b601aa586911b3ed65fe16","tid":1816981,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:12:22.000Z","msg":"推個"},{"pid":"f696aa22e5bdf634bf82dd5615c0ad668148880f","tid":1816981,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada681f5dade17e452e48cf4cacf4f84dc6603a3","tid":1816981,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abe47c7619fb43107a0483313aaa624705496d6","tid":1816981,"uid":271690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"08eea6a06f810b3f663fdcfaffc6de85e7f4bf81","tid":1816981,"uid":67231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:21:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9c14e7aceb79ba9740ee8d1fe53b8a83d7bc7c24","tid":1816981,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d753a2abb34fba15fdc812d392b249be47c123","tid":1816981,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb24c56c16931615394e3b9d735c826af2fa3ff","tid":1816981,"uid":302588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:29:30.000Z","msg":"點分邊個係手足，邊個係鬼？<br />\n<br />\n分唔到即係會捉錯，仲捉嚟做乜？"},{"pid":"09704822b3ef112547d52e44fc34a2becd619c78","tid":1816981,"uid":97704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:31:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cbd73b77f7299a493582c8f91447faed4f8d840","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beb24c56c16931615394e3b9d735c826af2fa3ff","tid":1816981,"uid":302588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:29:30.000Z","msg":"點分邊個係手足，邊個係鬼？<br />\n<br />\n分唔到即係會捉錯，仲捉嚟做乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個我都覺得係一個好大嘅問題，真心駁唔到。所以先要有一套系統去分辨。我地唔係一直都係用創意嚟制勝咩，今次又可能都會諗到一個方法保護到手足之餘又會刮到d鬼出嚟。"},{"pid":"0ed1caaaaed0923bd95bddbc68e08069ffc693a5","tid":1816981,"uid":211848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:37:38.000Z","msg":"推左先<br />\n講得幾好<br />\n聽朝幫手度度"},{"pid":"01e8e4c60b35a3f26b753aecf4488b04ed1097af","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ed1caaaaed0923bd95bddbc68e08069ffc693a5","tid":1816981,"uid":211848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:37:38.000Z","msg":"推左先<br />\n講得幾好<br />\n聽朝幫手度度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感謝手足"},{"pid":"4df9c72c6ed76ef5ee459cf92c5d06f46366de12","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:41:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bba343ea8bde40f8544dc1dc4ae52e7c3d9c5462","tid":1816981,"uid":263935,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T18:02:09.000Z","msg":"老老實實，我唔主張捉鬼，比你捉到真係鬼，夠膽打撚到佢變豬頭咩？我當你夠膽，家下啲鬼一係好撚多人，一係有槍，主動捉鬼加速班狗咬人既時間同力度，手足死傷慘重。<br />\n我覺得阻嚇性就真既，有狗落單，手足自然會識處理，一定要拉走晒啲左膠，包括fa，（我唔係屌fa，佢地既角色立場我理解明白，佢比人拉開既話就同佢地既立場冇衝突），比足夠既空間手足處理，增加做鬼既壓力，鬼既神情同果種緊張令手足更易察覺同防範。<br />\n捉鬼既風氣不可長，亦要全世界反捉鬼。好多年紀大啲既和理非唔好話連登，連fb都少睇，如果全世界既風氣都係唔捉鬼，佢地自然唔會捉，減低前線壓力，同避免捉錯鬼。如果唔係既話，佢地會覺得捉鬼就係保護細路，但事實係害緊手足。<br />\n總結，反對捉鬼風氣。"},{"pid":"d147798cc47853cdef5f2bedbd2fe67c5bba883a","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bba343ea8bde40f8544dc1dc4ae52e7c3d9c5462","tid":1816981,"uid":263935,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T18:02:09.000Z","msg":"老老實實，我唔主張捉鬼，比你捉到真係鬼，夠膽打撚到佢變豬頭咩？我當你夠膽，家下啲鬼一係好撚多人，一係有槍，主動捉鬼加速班狗咬人既時間同力度，手足死傷慘重。<br />\n我覺得阻嚇性就真既，有狗落單，手足自然會識處理，一定要拉走晒啲左膠，包括fa，（我唔係屌fa，佢地既角色立場我理解明白，佢比人拉開既話就同佢地既立場冇衝突），比足夠既空間手足處理，增加做鬼既壓力，鬼既神情同果種緊張令手足更易察覺同防範。<br />\n捉鬼既風氣不可長，亦要全世界反捉鬼。好多年紀大啲既和理非唔好話連登，連fb都少睇，如果全世界既風氣都係唔捉鬼，佢地自然唔會捉，減低前線壓力，同避免捉錯鬼。如果唔係既話，佢地會覺得捉鬼就係保護細路，但事實係害緊手足。<br />\n總結，反對捉鬼風氣。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T18:34:02.000Z","msg":"但係咁樣點樣去解決d鬼越嚟越多嘅問題？佢地唔會因為我地唔捉而唔放鬼。我覺得重點係，捉完要敢打波，之前捉完，全部人企撚晒係到，淨係識係到叫死黑警，完全比晒時間佢地搵backup。所以和理非乜冇野裝都冇就唔好捉，因為捉完都做唔到d咩。"},{"pid":"192a66bc999440fc4dedf08fcf790e09fbef0e3b","tid":1816981,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T00:30:06.000Z","msg":"呢個的確好難拆"},{"pid":"2935c1e0c6521d055779903f0ee7e84b87bc9a86","tid":1816981,"uid":200575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:11:55.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n雖然實行起黎好難好難好撚難<br />\n但思路正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62cc15170ba27d23811bbbd6ddb8c30bfed87492","tid":1816981,"uid":160363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c48d050e551b36d42b5df3a36d75998f2b590233","tid":1816981,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:36:07.000Z","msg":"樓主就係鬼！<img src=\"/a